<div class=" v-align text-center">
  <h4> So, ready to start to </h4>
  <h4><%= @task.name %> ?</h4><br>
  <p> Great! </p>
  <p>I'll reminding you of it </p>
  <p><%= @task.frequency %></p>
  <p> In the <%= @task.time_slot %></p>
  <p> At the distance of <%= @task.distance %></p>
  <div class="text-center">
    <%= link_to "Edit your task", edit_task_path(@task), class: "btn btn-primary btn-form" %>
    <%= link_to "All good? Ready!", dashboard_index_path, class: "btn btn-primary btn-form" %>
      <p class="btn btn-default btn-form">
        <%= link_to "Delete task", task_path(@task), :method => :delete,
          :class => 'btn-link' %>
      </p>
  </div>
  <p>“We become what we repeatedly do.”</p>
  <p> Sean Covey</p>
</div>
